{"tid":1943900,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"生存係一切苦難嘅根源","createTime":"2020-03-26T04:58:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-26T06:30:38.000Z","uid":269148,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"1af3ce2e7ff1c31dd29cbae4b6a17de10b668128","tid":1943900,"uid":269148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T04:58:47.000Z","msg":"同不同意<br />\n生存先有一切生理上心理上嘅慾望<br />\n肚餓帶嚟嘅痛苦急屎急尿帶嚟嘅痛苦<br />\n性慾物慾帶嚟痛苦<br />\n但一切都基於生存且有意識嘅前提底下<br />\n就算所謂快樂都只係痛苦得到舒緩<br />\n慾望暫時得到解決嘅感覺<br />\n快樂只係相對少痛苦<br />\n人出世前係無痛苦快樂嘅意識"},{"pid":"abbc7cbdb08078e82c7d69c6a3ca08e08c713dbc","tid":1943900,"uid":64882,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T05:00:20.000Z","msg":"我同意 咁樓主準備死未"},{"pid":"a8d91dc864fe1398c5d1a6c74418b96207324f26","tid":1943900,"uid":232250,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T05:01:10.000Z","msg":"睇通哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7e5a4bb78a9074ae06994cd7ac836ed2d4f3743","tid":1943900,"uid":269148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"abbc7cbdb08078e82c7d69c6a3ca08e08c713dbc","tid":1943900,"uid":64882,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T05:00:20.000Z","msg":"我同意 咁樓主準備死未"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T05:09:01.000Z","msg":"未想死住<br />\n我想得到生存嘅答案<br />\n要承受生存帶嚟嘅苦難<br />\n至少要比我有生存嘅原因同意義"},{"pid":"42894faf375e7daba16cfb0f09eb2293d2249f8a","tid":1943900,"uid":347687,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T05:29:58.000Z","msg":"生存係一啖砂糖十啖屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"570f02a52c3d5e5edf22f06f77686910d1fb85c7","tid":1943900,"uid":64882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b7e5a4bb78a9074ae06994cd7ac836ed2d4f3743","tid":1943900,"uid":269148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"abbc7cbdb08078e82c7d69c6a3ca08e08c713dbc","tid":1943900,"uid":64882,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T05:00:20.000Z","